%% KubeRay Operator - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant GW as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Dashboard as Ray Head Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    participant Operator as KubeRay Operator<br/>opendatahub namespace
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant CertMgr as cert-manager
    participant Workers as Ray Worker Pods<br/>10001/TCP, 6379/TCP

    Note over User, Dashboard: Flow 1: User Accesses Ray Dashboard (RHOAI 3.x)
    User->>GW: GET /ray/{ns}/{cluster}<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    GW->>GW: HTTPRoute match<br/>/ray/{ns}/{cluster}
    GW->>KRBP: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS
    KRBP->>KRBP: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(pods/get in cluster ns)
    KRBP->>Dashboard: Proxy to dashboard<br/>HTTP/8265, plaintext (localhost)
    Dashboard-->>KRBP: Dashboard response
    KRBP-->>GW: Response
    GW-->>User: HTML/JSON Response

    Note over Operator, K8sAPI: Flow 2: RayJob Submission
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch RayJob CR<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: RayJob event
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster CR
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create K8s batch Job<br/>(submitter)
    Note over K8sAPI: Job pod starts
    K8sAPI->>Dashboard: Job submitter connects<br/>HTTP/8265, plaintext/mTLS

    Note over Operator, CertMgr: Flow 3: mTLS Certificate Provisioning
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create SelfSigned Issuer<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    CertMgr->>CertMgr: Generate CA Certificate
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create CA Issuer
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Head Certificate<br/>(with pod IPs as SANs)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Worker Certificate<br/>(with pod IPs as SANs)
    CertMgr-->>K8sAPI: Secrets created
    Dashboard->>Workers: mTLS communication<br/>gRPC/10001, 6379<br/>cert-manager CA certs
    Workers-->>Dashboard: mTLS response
